						<summary>

						<p>Hero-stone set up in the temple of Rāmasvāmin.</p>						

						<p>12th century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This damaged inscription refers to a feudatory bearing the title <hi rend="italic">Banavāsi-puravarādhīsvara</hi> and to a certain <hi rend="italic">anādiyagrahāra.</hi></p>						

						<p>The characters belong to about 12th century A.D.</p>						

						</summary>
